="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/Ph%E1%BB%8Dc-nhung-nh%C3%A2n/poem-2NYSpqJiCjEUIB2gsgV6qA">Phọc nhung nhân - 縛戎人</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4ng-B%E1%BA%A3n-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/S%C6%A1n-c%C6%B0-b%C3%A1ch-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-k%E1%BB%B3-002/poem-gVPVV6JCkbJnd_n4VuaGZw">Sơn cư bách vịnh kỳ 002 - 山居百詠其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4ng-B%E1%BA%A3n-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-jnvtlp5PrNS3FoOBBGt7-w">Tông Bản thiền sư</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A2n-Kh%C3%AD-T%E1%BA%ADt/Thu%E1%BB%B7-long-ng%C3%A2m-Vi-H%C3%A0n-Nam-Gi%E1%BA%A3n-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-th%C6%B0-th%E1%BB%8D-Gi%C3%A1p-Th%C3%ACn-tu%E1%BA%BF/poem-xHy7QQigZcNKYCKj2TW_jA">Thuỷ long ngâm - Vi Hàn Nam Giản thượng thư thọ Giáp Thìn tuế - 水龍吟－為韓南澗尚書壽甲辰歲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A2n-Kh%C3%AD-T%E1%BA%ADt/author-cR0yq4BrF6xGIKZCvJGLSA">Tân Khí Tật</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/V%C3%B4-gia-bi%E1%BB%87t/poem-Lmk1srGEtNuIi0hYAVvAPA">Vô gia biệt - 無家別</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
